snippet.title: NBA players texted me 'what about Melo?' after Joe Johnson got signed - Rachel Nichols | The Jump
snippet.description:
In her daily monologue, Rachel Nichols discusses what Joe Johnson signing with the Detroit Pistons could mean for the future of Carmelo Anthony, who has yet to find an NBA team despite his All-Star tenure with teams like the Denver Nuggets and New York Knicks. She is then (4:08) joined by Dave McMenamin and Richard Jefferson discuss why Melo hasn't been signed yet.
